      "layer": 1,
      "layer_name": "Domain Knowledge (This Company)",
      "header": "AI Health Dashboard & Monitoring (LIVE Feb 11, 2026)",
      "content": "## AI Health Dashboard & Monitoring (LIVE Feb 11, 2026)\n- **Route**: `/admin/ai-health` (session-protected) — 10 module cards + 7 AI modality cards + 11 AI module rows + call distribution\n- **Tabs**: Overview (cards), Status (health banner, 12 stat cards, DB pool gauge, slow queries, token budget per-provider, activity feed), Metrics (CPU/memory/DB/API latency percentiles), AI Monitoring (budget predictions, hourly usage chart, model performance, module cost breakdown, real-time call log), Prompts (registry, version history, perf metrics), Activity Feed (60+ route patterns)\n- **Backend collectors**: `db.js` (query tracking, pool %), `metrics-collector.js` (HTTP connections), `token-budget.js` (per-provider), `ai-call-logger.js` (every call: module/provider/model/tokens/latency/cost/fallback)\n- **Budget prediction**: Burn rate calculation, forecasts 100K daily exhaustion time\n- **Priority-based throttling**: Critical modules (interviews, assessments) never throttled; low-priority auto-throttled at 80%+ budget\n- **13 new API endpoints**: `/api/ai-health/*` suite for usage, budget, logs, models, predictions, prompts, A/B tests, natural language query",
      "relevance": "42%"
    },
    {
      "layer": 3,
      "layer_name": "Cross-Company Patterns",
      "header": "Current Cross-Company Patterns (engineering) (9847 tokens)",
      "content": "## Current Cross-Company Patterns (engineering) (9847 tokens)",
      "relevance": "40%"
    }
  ]
}

